大專生研習、實習 (Student Research Learning)


NHRI大專生暑期研習計畫 (Undergraduate Student Summer Research Program)


2016 NHRI暑期研習成果競賽結果公告 Summer research report contest RESULT




































　











NHRI大專生暑期研習計畫(NHRI Undergraduate Student Summer Research Program)



目的(Objectives)：
      鼓勵公私立大專院校學生至本院研習，參與研究計畫，瞭解生物醫藥領域之研究方法，以培養並啟發具潛力之之生物醫學年輕研究人才。In order to train and inspire young potential biomedical research talent, we welcome and encourage undergraduate students to participate in biomedical research projects of NHRI.
 
資格(Qualification)：
      國內外公私立大專院校在學學生，獲得本院專任助研究員以上之研究人員(以下簡稱研究指導員)同意指導暑期研習者。Domestic and overseas undergraduate students who have obtained the summer research advising approval from any NHRI full-time principal investigator are qualified. 
 
參與研究期間(Research Period)：
      每年6月20日至同年9月20日以內，至少二個月。At least two months from June 20 to September 20 in the same year.
 
研習補助(Research Subsidy)：每人新台幣1萬元。NT $ 10,000 per student.
 
研習成果報告比賽(Summer research report contest)：
      無論是否申請研習補助皆可參加，擇優3名給予獎勵新台幣5000元。All the program participants are eligible to join the contest. Three best selects will receive a NT$5,000 award each.
 
申請方式(Application)：
      備齊下列資料各乙份，送本院學務辦公室辦理審查。For applying, please provide one copy each of the following documents to the NHRI Student Affairs Office for review.
(一)     國家衛生研究院大專生暑期研習申請表NHRI Undergraduate Student Summer Research Application form (應先完成研習指導教師、學校系所主管、研習單位主管簽核 After signed by instrucor, Head of School Department, and Director of NHRI Department)
(二)     學生證正反面影印本 Photocopy of both sides of student ID card
(三)     國民身分證正反面影印本 Photocopy of passport or resident permit
(四)     近期彩色照片(製作本院識別證用) Soft copy of a recent color passport photo
(五)     歷年成績單Transcript
(六)     學生本人存摺帳號影本(任何銀行皆可) Photocopy of applicant’s bankbook with account No. information shown on it (any bank in Taiwan). 
(七)   學生無專職工作聲明書 NO full-time work declaration
 
受理申請期間(Application Deadline)：
      每年5月1日至5月20日止，以送達時間為準，逾期恕不補助。Applications received from May 1 to May 20 by the Office are eligible for applying program subsidy.
外籍學生申請短期研習註意事項 
        (Precautions for Foreign students short-term study application)
如不具台灣國籍需申請研習簽證者，請務必於研習開始60天前填妥外籍學生短期研習申請並繳附相關文件，待接獲本院核發之外籍學生研習同意書後，再向台灣各駐外館處辦理研習簽證申請。Foreign students please deliver “Foreign Student Short-term Research Application” form and related documents 60 days before beginning study. After receiving NHRI Foreign Student Research and Study Consent, carry on Taiwan Visitor VISA for Internship application at our overseas missions (website: https://visawebapp.boca.gov.tw). 
 
本院聯絡人(NHRI Contact Information)：
      學務辦公室瞿小姐Mrs. Sandy Chu at the Student Affairs Office，電話(phone)：+886-37-246166 #31102，E-mail：970322@nhri.org.tw。 












































 
 
 


 
